body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is Michael Martin and I'm calling from Secure Auto Solutions. May I ask for your name?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my name is Judith Williams.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Judith. Can I kindly ask for your date of birth?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, it's the ninth of May, nineteen seven five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Judith. I also need your home address for our records. Could you provide that for me, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my address is eighty three Apple Street, Laurel City.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing the information, Judith. Is there anything specific you'd like assistance with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm having some security concerns related to my car purchase at your dealership.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Judith. Rest assured, we'll address your concerns promptly. Thank you for bringing this to our attention.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Judith. We appreciate your patience. Have a great day.
